1
00:01:33,120 --> 00:01:33,880
Who is it?

2
00:01:34,000 --> 00:01:34,560
It's me.

3
00:01:49,080 --> 00:01:49,920
Zhinian.

4
00:01:50,160 --> 00:01:51,160
How did you get in?

5
00:01:51,360 --> 00:01:52,720
I climbed over the wall.

6
00:01:55,800 --> 00:01:56,440
Zhinian,

7
00:01:56,960 --> 00:01:57,890
why are you here?

8
00:01:58,160 --> 00:01:59,560
What are you trying to do?

9
00:02:00,360 --> 00:02:01,600
I have so many things to ask you,

10
00:02:01,600 --> 00:02:02,860
and so much to tell you.

11
00:02:03,160 --> 00:02:04,560
Tomorrow is the wedding.

12
00:02:04,720 --> 00:02:06,050
I can't wait any longer.

13
00:02:06,120 --> 00:02:07,720
Zhinian, calm down.

14
00:02:08,479 --> 00:02:09,740
What do you want to say?

15
00:02:10,039 --> 00:02:10,919
I am listening.

16
00:02:12,240 --> 00:02:12,840
Linglong.

17
00:02:13,840 --> 00:02:16,040
Do you really like that young master of the Zhang family?

18
00:02:16,040 --> 00:02:17,120
Of course not.

19
00:02:18,560 --> 00:02:20,020
The person I want to marry,

20
00:02:20,120 --> 00:02:21,120
is only one.

21
00:02:30,560 --> 00:02:31,440
This is...

22
00:02:33,440 --> 00:02:34,500
Let me put it on you.

23
00:02:50,760 --> 00:02:51,760
So beautiful.

24
00:03:00,040 --> 00:03:01,640
Are you willing to go with me?

25
00:03:03,240 --> 00:03:04,480
Now I am an official.

26
00:03:05,200 --> 00:03:06,840
We can find a place with no one around,

27
00:03:06,840 --> 00:03:07,960
and live in mutual respect,

28
00:03:07,960 --> 00:03:09,490
staying together forever.

29
00:03:09,760 --> 00:03:10,490
How about it?

30
00:03:16,640 --> 00:03:18,440
How I wish I could just walk away.

31
00:03:19,240 --> 00:03:20,360
But I can't.

32
00:03:21,160 --> 00:03:21,720
For my mother,

33
00:03:21,720 --> 00:03:22,720
for the Hu family,

34
00:03:23,880 --> 00:03:25,600
and for the things I must do.

35
00:03:31,960 --> 00:03:33,360
Tomorrow is the wedding.

36
00:03:33,680 --> 00:03:35,940
If you and I could stay together forever,

37
00:03:36,560 --> 00:03:38,160
how wonderful that would be.

38
00:03:45,280 --> 00:03:46,280
Why not?

39
00:03:48,000 --> 00:03:48,800
Zhinian,

40
00:03:49,880 --> 00:03:51,740
are you willing to be here with me,

41
00:03:53,079 --> 00:03:54,200
and get married?

42
00:03:56,920 --> 00:03:57,960
I, Xu Zhinian,

43
00:03:59,200 --> 00:04:00,460
couldn't ask for more.

44
00:04:17,200 --> 00:04:19,480
First bow to heaven and earth.

45
00:04:26,840 --> 00:04:29,320
Second bow to parents.

46
00:04:41,880 --> 00:04:44,720
Husband and wife bow to each other.

47
00:04:58,680 --> 00:05:00,200
Bound together as mountains and seas,

48
00:05:00,200 --> 00:05:01,600
two hearts united as one.

49
00:05:02,040 --> 00:05:03,120
In this life,

50
00:05:03,120 --> 00:05:04,320
when it comes to love,

51
00:05:04,800 --> 00:05:05,920
I have no regrets.

52
00:05:07,960 --> 00:05:08,960
So do I.

53
00:05:18,520 --> 00:05:19,800
A bunch of lowly servants,

54
00:05:19,800 --> 00:05:21,280
dare to run wild in my house!

55
00:05:21,280 --> 00:05:22,000
Madam.

56
00:05:22,160 --> 00:05:22,690
Zhinian,

57
00:05:22,840 --> 00:05:23,500
go quickly!

58
00:05:25,600 --> 00:05:26,200
Linglong!

59
00:05:26,600 --> 00:05:28,460
I will come back for you tomorrow!

60
00:05:28,840 --> 00:05:29,600
Zhinian,

61
00:05:29,880 --> 00:05:31,940
don't ruin your future because of me.

62
00:05:32,600 --> 00:05:33,040
No,

63
00:05:33,600 --> 00:05:34,480
I will be back!

64
00:05:37,159 --> 00:05:37,840
Zhinian,

65
00:05:38,240 --> 00:05:39,300
I have my own plans.

66
00:05:39,400 --> 00:05:40,930
You must not act on your own.

67
00:05:41,120 --> 00:05:42,680
If you continue to be so unruly,

68
00:05:42,680 --> 00:05:44,640
I will go to the Zhang family for an explanation!

69
00:05:44,640 --> 00:05:45,240
Go now!

70
00:06:12,120 --> 00:06:12,880
Hu Linglong,

71
00:06:13,080 --> 00:06:14,680
what are you thinking about?

72
00:06:19,800 --> 00:06:21,320
Actually, since that day in the ancestral hall,

73
00:06:21,320 --> 00:06:23,520
after seeing my father's suicide note,

74
00:06:23,920 --> 00:06:26,050
I have been thinking about a question.

75
00:06:27,240 --> 00:06:28,640
Why would he, on his suicide note,

76
00:06:28,640 --> 00:06:29,840
write my real name?

77
00:06:31,520 --> 00:06:33,200
When he was still alive,

78
00:06:33,200 --> 00:06:34,930
he racked his brains every day,

79
00:06:35,040 --> 00:06:35,960
about me,

80
00:06:35,960 --> 00:06:38,000
carefully weaving a huge lie.

81
00:06:38,280 --> 00:06:39,480
But he knew well

82
00:06:40,200 --> 00:06:42,240
that the suicide note would be seen by the clan elders,

83
00:06:42,240 --> 00:06:44,280
yet he still wrote my real name on it,

84
00:06:45,800 --> 00:06:48,330
letting his years of hard work go up in flames.

85
00:06:48,800 --> 00:06:49,960
I don't understand.

86
00:06:53,040 --> 00:06:54,640
How many things in this world

87
00:06:54,680 --> 00:06:56,640
can we understand the meaning of

88
00:06:56,640 --> 00:06:58,360
before we actually do them?

89
00:06:59,040 --> 00:06:59,960
Sometimes,

90
00:07:00,280 --> 00:07:01,610
the result comes first,

91
00:07:01,680 --> 00:07:02,740
and then the cause.

92
00:07:03,760 --> 00:07:05,200
Perhaps your father did this

93
00:07:05,200 --> 00:07:06,720
for a special reason.

94
00:07:07,760 --> 00:07:08,600
Or perhaps

95
00:07:08,920 --> 00:07:10,380
there's no meaning at all,

96
00:07:10,800 --> 00:07:12,400
just following his heart.

97
00:07:13,680 --> 00:07:15,120
Following his heart.

98
00:07:33,880 --> 00:07:34,640
Hu Linglong,

99
00:07:35,080 --> 00:07:38,080
you aren't really planning to kill yourself, are you?

100
00:07:38,159 --> 00:07:38,600
Hey,

101
00:07:38,600 --> 00:07:39,400
Hu Linglong,

102
00:07:39,400 --> 00:07:40,480
say something!

103
00:08:05,000 --> 00:08:05,800
Zhinian,

104
00:08:05,800 --> 00:08:07,080
I have my own plans.

105
00:08:07,360 --> 00:08:08,890
You must not act on your own.

106
00:08:11,880 --> 00:08:12,640
Mr. Zhang,

107
00:08:12,640 --> 00:08:13,680
you need to pick up the bride.

108
00:08:13,680 --> 00:08:15,080
If you don't, you'll miss the auspicious time.

109
00:08:15,080 --> 00:08:15,920
Do it now.

110
00:08:15,920 --> 00:08:17,000
It's raining, I'm not going!

111
00:08:17,000 --> 00:08:18,360
I said I'm not going!

112
00:08:18,360 --> 00:08:19,320
I want to go home!

113
00:08:19,640 --> 00:08:20,800
Oh, what are you doing?

114
00:08:20,800 --> 00:08:21,400
I want to go home!

115
00:08:21,400 --> 00:08:22,560
What are you doing?

116
00:08:22,840 --> 00:08:23,200
Ah!

117
00:08:24,280 --> 00:08:24,680
Dad!

118
00:08:26,360 --> 00:08:27,320
I want to go home!

119
00:08:28,600 --> 00:08:29,560
It's raining.

120
00:08:30,080 --> 00:08:31,480
Let me out!

121
00:08:31,480 --> 00:08:32,679
I want my mom!

122
00:08:32,679 --> 00:08:33,640
What on earth is going on?

123
00:08:33,640 --> 00:08:35,080
It suddenly started raining,

124
00:08:35,080 --> 00:08:37,080
and Mr. Zhang refuses to pick up the bride.

125
00:08:37,080 --> 00:08:37,940
Look at this...

126
00:08:38,000 --> 00:08:39,000
I want to go home!

127
00:08:39,919 --> 00:08:40,679
Alas!

128
00:08:41,159 --> 00:08:42,000
Mr. Zhang,

129
00:08:42,120 --> 00:08:43,679
today is your big day.

130
00:08:43,880 --> 00:08:45,360
I said I'm not going!

131
00:08:45,360 --> 00:08:46,880
It's raining, I want to go home!

132
00:08:46,880 --> 00:08:47,920
You're getting a wife.

133
00:08:47,920 --> 00:08:48,320
Ah.

134
00:08:48,840 --> 00:08:50,240
Someone to warm your bed,

135
00:08:50,240 --> 00:08:50,760
isn't that nice?

136
00:08:50,760 --> 00:08:51,600
Ah, no!

137
00:08:52,240 --> 00:08:52,880
Rain!

138
00:08:52,880 --> 00:08:54,480
You can't do anything right.

139
00:08:54,520 --> 00:08:55,040
Master.

140
00:08:55,160 --> 00:08:56,360
On the way to pick up the bride,

141
00:08:56,360 --> 00:08:57,480
a sudden downpour occurred.

142
00:08:57,480 --> 00:08:59,740
It's inauspicious to get married today.

143
00:09:00,400 --> 00:09:01,960
Who cares about auspiciousness?

144
00:09:01,960 --> 00:09:02,560
Today,

145
00:09:03,240 --> 00:09:05,170
whether it rains or pours daggers,

146
00:09:05,520 --> 00:09:06,320
this marriage

147
00:09:06,360 --> 00:09:07,290
must take place.

148
00:09:11,520 --> 00:09:12,040
Nian,

149
00:09:12,040 --> 00:09:12,960
what happened?

150
00:09:14,080 --> 00:09:14,540
Mother,

151
00:09:14,680 --> 00:09:15,960
why are you like this?

152
00:09:17,280 --> 00:09:17,740
Mother.

153
00:09:18,480 --> 00:09:18,760
I...

154
00:09:27,120 --> 00:09:28,320
Mr. Zhang.

155
00:09:28,360 --> 00:09:29,480
I want to go home

156
00:09:29,640 --> 00:09:30,570
and get married!

157
00:09:31,080 --> 00:09:31,720
Come on.

158
00:09:32,160 --> 00:09:32,800
Ouch!

159
00:09:32,800 --> 00:09:33,920
Come on, be good.

160
00:09:33,920 --> 00:09:35,040
Hey, be good.

161
00:09:36,720 --> 00:09:38,520
Come on.

162
00:09:41,760 --> 00:09:43,160
Help Mr. Zhang get on the horse.

163
00:09:43,160 --> 00:09:43,920
Yes, right.

164
00:09:43,920 --> 00:09:44,840
Hey.

165
00:09:45,160 --> 00:09:46,360
Sit tight.

166
00:09:46,560 --> 00:09:47,600
Okay.

167
00:09:48,040 --> 00:09:48,760
Come on.

168
00:09:49,000 --> 00:09:50,000
Start playing the music!

169
00:09:50,000 --> 00:09:51,260
Let's liven things up!

170
00:09:51,560 --> 00:09:52,890
Come on, play the music!

171
00:09:53,440 --> 00:09:54,720
Liven things up!

172
00:09:56,320 --> 00:09:57,400
I'll leave this to you.

173
00:09:57,400 --> 00:09:57,840
Okay.

174
00:09:58,280 --> 00:09:58,810
Be smart.

175
00:10:01,040 --> 00:10:02,840
Escort the bride to her wedding!

176
00:10:28,480 --> 00:10:29,840
Is it about Qingyun?

177
00:10:31,200 --> 00:10:31,760
No,

178
00:10:31,960 --> 00:10:33,690
it's about Linglong, isn't it?

179
00:10:39,720 --> 00:10:41,560
I hear people talking about

180
00:10:41,560 --> 00:10:43,800
Linglong every day outside,

181
00:10:44,160 --> 00:10:46,960
but you have never mentioned it to me even once.

182
00:10:47,480 --> 00:10:50,320
You grew up by my side since you were a child.

183
00:10:51,280 --> 00:10:54,320
How could I not know what you're thinking?

184
00:10:55,680 --> 00:10:57,140
Between you and Linglong,

185
00:10:57,160 --> 00:10:59,480
you have long

186
00:10:59,560 --> 00:11:01,160
been in love with each other.

187
00:11:01,600 --> 00:11:02,400
Today

188
00:11:03,000 --> 00:11:06,400
is the wedding day of Linglong and Mr. Zhang.

189
00:11:06,960 --> 00:11:07,680
Right?

190
00:11:08,000 --> 00:11:08,760
Yes.

191
00:11:10,040 --> 00:11:10,760
Mother.

192
00:11:11,480 --> 00:11:13,480
Linglong was forced to marry him.

193
00:11:13,840 --> 00:11:15,040
If she marries Mr. Zhang,

194
00:11:15,040 --> 00:11:16,080
she will be stepping into a cage

195
00:11:16,080 --> 00:11:18,240
that she may never escape in her lifetime.

196
00:11:18,240 --> 00:11:19,570
How can I just watch her?

197
00:11:24,320 --> 00:11:25,680
Go, Zhinian.

198
00:11:27,680 --> 00:11:28,280
Mother,

199
00:11:28,840 --> 00:11:30,370
you know what I'm thinking.

200
00:11:32,320 --> 00:11:33,320
Don't worry about

201
00:11:33,320 --> 00:11:34,560
your father.

202
00:11:34,560 --> 00:11:35,520
I'm here for you.

203
00:11:40,040 --> 00:11:40,560
Mother.

204
00:11:42,000 --> 00:11:43,660
Don't let yourself regret it.

205
00:11:45,480 --> 00:11:46,720
Go, Zhinian.

206
00:11:49,840 --> 00:11:50,120
Go.

207
00:12:23,880 --> 00:12:24,800
No, no.

208
00:12:24,800 --> 00:12:25,920
The way Hu Linglong is acting,

209
00:12:25,920 --> 00:12:26,560
she clearly wants to fight to the death with

210
00:12:26,560 --> 00:12:28,520
Hu Wenyi and Mr. Zhang.

211
00:12:29,000 --> 00:12:29,960
If she dies,

212
00:12:30,320 --> 00:12:31,980
does that mean I can't go back?

213
00:12:47,520 --> 00:12:49,040
How did I end up here?

214
00:12:49,360 --> 00:12:50,200
Qiao Xin,

215
00:12:50,200 --> 00:12:51,660
you broke your oath again.

216
00:12:52,360 --> 00:12:54,090
I will never believe you again.

217
00:12:54,360 --> 00:12:55,520
You're determined to die,

218
00:12:55,520 --> 00:12:57,120
so why talk about the future?

219
00:12:57,440 --> 00:12:59,280
I was the one who made the oath in the ancestral hall,

220
00:12:59,280 --> 00:13:01,000
and I was the one who got you into trouble.

221
00:13:01,000 --> 00:13:01,760
What happened today,

222
00:13:01,760 --> 00:13:03,000
I will definitely help you solve it.

223
00:13:03,000 --> 00:13:03,800
Solve it?

224
00:13:03,800 --> 00:13:05,000
How will you solve it?

225
00:13:05,640 --> 00:13:06,800
Of course,

226
00:13:06,800 --> 00:13:07,760
by running away from the wedding.
